# CSS Box Model

Every HTML element is a box.

## Components

1. Content
2. Padding
3. Border
4. Margin

## Example

```css
div {
    width: 300px;
    padding: 20px;
    border: 2px solid black;
    margin: 20px;
}
```

## Box-Sizing

```css
* {
    box-sizing: border-box;
}
```

## Why Use Border-Box?

It keeps width calculations simple.

## Real-World Example

Used in responsive layouts and card designs.

## Summary

Understanding the box model is essential for layouts.
